INSERT INTO public.vacancy (id, about, broker, hours, location, posting_date, salary, title, vacancy_number, vacancyurl) VALUES ('8d938a66-1472-4644-9b18-7494b3503845', '<p>I am looking for a curious Model Data Analyst, who is looking forward to bringing the client''s global model data environment to the next level. From your thorough understanding of risk data, you''re able to see how the modelling team can be well serviced with high quality data marts to feed the risk models. Your technical and analytical skills enable you to pre-process the data before model development start using it. A successful candidate has proven experience in usage of risk data and querying tools (e.g. sql, SAS).</p>
