INSERT INTO public.vacancy (id, about, broker, hours, location, posting_date, salary, title, vacancy_number, vacancyurl) VALUES ('a98c75de-12dc-480c-980a-d10976897694', '<h1><strong>Senior front-End Developer</strong></h1>
<p>One of our rapidly growing clients in Almere is looking for a senior front-end developer. The organisation digitalizes product information and pictures of all products sold by companies like Albert Heijn, Jumbo and many more. Basically every product that is sold online has been digitalized by this particular client. They tend to expand to the entire Europe market since they have more than 95% of the Dutch market share.</p>
<p>As the front-end developer, you will be responsible for the front-end with one other front-end developer. The current development team consist of 5 developers in total. Your responsibility is to upgrade, built and also renew the front-end of their products. Therefore it''s necessary to have a strong knowledge and background within JavaScript and front-end development. My client has plans to scale up the development team, which is where you will play an important role as well.</p>
<p>You will be responsible for translating the front-end to their hardware and tools and the enhancement of the modern and complex applications. Read on for more information regarding the requirements and benefits:</p>
<h3> </h3>
<h3><strong>Required skills for the senior Front-End Developer:</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>Excellent experience with JavaScript</li>
<li>Experience with Frameworks/Libraries like Vue, React or Angular</li>
<li>Experience with MySQL, jQuery</li>
<li>Experience in working with a team</li>
<li>Be responsible for own work</li>
<li>Good English and/or Dutch communication skills</li>
<li>Independent/analytical/problem solving skills/critical/result driven</li>
</ul>
<h3> </h3>
<h3><strong>What do you get in return?</strong></h3>
<ul>
<li>Good salary</li>
<li>A challenging role within a company that is outperforming other companies in order to keep its market leading position</li>
<li>Extensive development and career opportunities</li>
<li>Chance to be responsible for the front-end</li>
<li>Informal and professional atmosphere and a pleasant work environment</li>
</ul>
<h3> </h3>
